I"<h2 style="font-family: Ergonomique Bold">The science behind note-taking: Preferences between handwriting and typing notes</h2>
<p>Nadwa Atwi. 04/23/2021</p>
<hr />

<p>Taking notes is one of the most important parts of the learning process. Students often spend a lot of time considering how to take notes, only to end up choosing a technique unfit for the material they’re tackling. So here we’ll be covering the pros and cons of each and discussing the right font-color combination for ideal note-taking.</p>
